  {
    "client_msg_id": "c3a5ea54-4b63-432f-8e84-94515482a8d5",
    "type": "message",
    "text": "Also RPA (robotic process automation), which enables scripting web and desktop apps for business use, is perhaps something that is related to this.\n\nRPA has evolved from test automation tools (think Selenium and similar tools). Many RPA tools have visual editors that let non-programmers record and script automations.\n\n<https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Robotic_process_automation>",
    "user": "UEQ7QL15F",
    "ts": "1646138350.849909",
    "team": "T5TCAFTA9",
    "user_team": "T5TCAFTA9",
